        <section name="Adding the plugin to your POM">
            <p>
               The Maven Site Indexer is a standard maven plugin. Download the code, mvn install it and then add the following to your pom.xml
            </p>
<source>
 &lt;plugin>
   &lt;groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId>
   &lt;artifactId>index&lt;/artifactId>
   &lt;version>0.0.1-SNAPSHOT&lt;/version>
   &lt;executions>
     &lt;execution>
       &lt;phase>site&lt;/phase>
       &lt;goals>
         &lt;goal>index&lt;/goal>
       &lt;/goals>
     &lt;/execution>
   &lt;/executions>
 &lt;/plugin></source>
		</section>
    </body>
